      public MotorConfig(double distanceFactor, double timeFactor, int currentLimit, double voltageCompensation, boolean inverted, NAR_Motor.Neutral mode, NAR_Motor.StatusFrames statusFrames)
      Creates a new motor config
      Parameters:
      distanceFactor - Factor to multiply distance units by, ie. rotations
      timeFactor - Factor to multiply time units by, ie. minutes
      currentLimit - The currentLimit for the motor
      inverted - Whether or not the motor is inverted.
      mode - Neutral mode for the motor.
      statusFrames - Status frames for the motor.
